  <brief_title>Exploratory Safety Study of ALD518 in Subjects With Steroid-refractory Acute Graft Versus Host Disease (GVHD)</brief_title>
  <acronym>ALD518-010</acronym>
  <official_title>An Exploratory Phase 1/2 Clinical Trial Evaluating ALD518 in Subjects With Glucocorticoid-Refractory Acute Graft vs. Host Disease (GVHD) After Allogeneic Hematopoietic Stem Cell Transplant (HSCT)</official_title>
