  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the safe and tolerable, biologically active, and
      potentially effective doses(s) of ALD518 in subjects with acute GVHD, who have failed to
      respond to glucocorticosteroids, for further investigation in Part B.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
